message.body: Morning! Just letting you guys know, Cassy and jimmy aren't coming tonight because she has to pick her brother up at the airport. I was also never 100% certain that Kimberlee would come, so worse comes to worse, it's the six of us....which isn't bad in the least
That's the six I was counting.
Yes. I'm so sorry! I was at the movies with crystal.
And my hunch was correct. Kim isn't coming. So it'll just be us 6
What time should we meet up?
Hey. Do you think you'll happen to be on time?
Hey. Okay, got a red light. In U. City. Will try to find parking on Sansom.
Okay. Sounds good. I called the restaurant and they said they'd hold our table.
